'''Solar Essence''' is a [[Monster Loot]] item which is dropped from the [[Ghost]], [[Bats|Iridium Bat]], [[Metal Head]], [[Metal Head (dangerous)]], [[Haunted Skull]], [[Squid Kid]], [[Squid Kid (dangerous)]], [[Mummy]], [[Hot Head]], and [[Blue Squid]]. [[Krobus]] also sells 10 a day for {{price|80}} each.  [[Sunfish]] may randomly produce a Solar Essence in a [[Fish Pond]] when the pond population reaches 10 fish.

